者会上鞠躬致歉。他说：“这是对客户信任的背叛。公司的制造基础已被动摇，情况严峻。”日本国土交通省要求IHI公司及其子公司调查此事，防止类似事件再次发生。 来源：上观新闻日本知名发动机制造商承认篡改数据超4000次"},"attached_info":"Cj8Imp+W68j26qBlEAMaCTEwNzYyNDU3OCC40KexBjAAODVAB3IJNjU0MDYwMjE3eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA=","detail_text":"88 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-f02139d7200da119b37e36262cf7e86f_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"8_1714101531.963652","card_id":"Q_68373340","target":{"id":68373340,"title":"人可以被驯化吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/68373340","type":"question","created":1511138689,"answer_count":103,"follower_count":244,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[404,994,1576,7998],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"Cj4Imp+W68j26qBlEAMaCDE5NTc4MDUxIIHLyNAFMAA49AFACHIINjgzNzMzNDB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"81 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"9_1714101531.963872","card_id":"Q_653974947","target":{"id":653974947,"title":"汉字为什么没有像韩文한이这种圆圈部首？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/653974947","type":"question","created":1713951096,"answer_count":84,"follower_count":190,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[1306,7499,19771,96818],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkAImp+W68j26qBlEAMaCTEwNzYwNTUxNSD4oqOxBjAAOL4BQAlyCTY1Mzk3NDk0N3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"79 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-dec1e9da604cd6bceb7d01d016583d52_720w.webp?source=1def8aca"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"10_1714101531.964068","c